        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 7 at 4:44AM EDT by NWS Upton NY</headline>
        <description>Areas of fog will be locally dense this evening across southern
Connecticut with visibilities falling below a quarter mile, at
times. This could make for hazardous driving during the morning
commute. Motorists are urged to slow down and use caution.

Visibilities are expected to improve by 8am.
</description>
